---
title: Italy's Cheesy Parmigiana Sausage Burgers with Tomato Sauce and Chips
description: "Forza Azzurri!" Show your support this Six Nations with burgers inspired by each team's homeland! An homage to the classic Italian dish, this Cheesy Parmigiana Sausage Burger is best served pitch-side with vibrant green pesto and chips.
